verses.verse: The LORD is king! He is robed in majesty. Indeed, the LORD is robed in majesty and armed with strength. The world stands firm and cannot be shaken.
Your throne, O LORD, has stood from time immemorial. You yourself are from the everlasting past.
The floods have risen up, O LORD. The floods have roared like thunder; the floods have lifted their pounding waves.
But mightier than the violent raging of the seas, mightier than the breakers on the shoreâ€” the LORD above is mightier than these!
Your royal laws cannot be changed. Your reign, O LORD, is holy forever and ever.
